Title: Golden Bird
Plot: Al and Carrie investigate the murder of a teen who seemed to have no enemies. Meanwhile, Carrie looks to her estranged aunt for help with the investigation into her sister's murder.
GuestStars: Deanna Dunagan, Marilu Henner, Derek Cecil, Kellie Overbey, Jack Gwaltney, Anna Friedman, Peter Benson, Drew McVety, Aaron Sauter, Anne Clare Gibbons-Brown, Jamil Mena, Mark Zeisler, Anna Rose Hopkins
